          "username": "danowak"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-04-30 11:02:07.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n(1 comment)\n\nI think, the approach proposed here is not future-proof.\nIt will require immediate refactoring in order to keep the SO/DMaaP client generic. At this moment, it tends to contain some BBS-specific behaviors.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      }
